data.description: Better than brand new, this year-old home has gorgeous additions and upgrades throughout. This 3 bedroom/2 bath home ALSO has an office. The light and bright open floor plan boasts a lovely kitchen with an oversized island, granite countertops, custom backsplash and a walk in pantry. The home is adorned with quality interior shutters throughout. The owners suite offers a large bedroom, dual vanities, walk in shower & a large closet with all of the built-in bells & whistles. Down a separate hall you will find two additional bedrooms and a guest bath. The covered back patio and backyard landscaping are perfect for outdoor entertaining. Home also offers a large laundry room w/extra storage, a whole house water filtration system, new high end carpeting in bedrooms, extensive back landscapin
